Package com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.graphs.dynamicProgramming.knapsack

Class Graph

java.lang.Object
com.phasmidsoftware.dsaipg.graphs.dynamicProgramming.knapsack.Graph
public class Graph extends Object
The Graph class represents a directed graph. It supports adding vertices, adding edges between vertices, and provides access to various graph properties such as the number of vertices, the number of edges, and adjacency relationships. The graph is represented using an adjacency list, where each vertex is associated with a list of its adjacent edges.
